ActIndian Act
PrecisOrder authorizing entry into a SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT with the SHXWHA:Y VILLAGE, in the Province of British Columbia. The agreement provides that the Shxwha:y Village will receive compensation from Canada, the province of British Columbia, and the City of Chilliwack for the loss of land on Shxwha:y Indian Reserve No. 5.
